{
  "texts": [
    "The five parts are:",
    "• The current input of the Time-mix block x t;",
    "• The current input of the Channel-mix block y t;",
    "• The numerator of the W KV value a ′ t, as defined in equation (26); • The denominator of the W KV value b ′ t, as defined in equation (27); • An auxiliary state p t in (28), which is used for W KV computation to maintain numerical precision.",
    "Which yields a total size of 5DL parameters."
  ]
}